@startuml
title Backend CI/CD (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor Dev
participant "GitHub Repo" as Repo
participant "GitHub Actions\nfreshfood-ci-cd" as GHA
participant "backend-ci\n(Python 3.10)" as BCI
participant "build-and-publish-images" as CD
database "GHCR" as GHCR

Dev -> Repo: Push / Open PR
Repo -> GHA: Trigger workflow\n(path includes test1/backend/**)
GHA -> BCI: Checkout\npip install -r requirements.txt\npytest -q tests
BCI --> GHA: pass/fail

alt Event = push AND backend-ci pass\n(and frontend-ci pass)
  GHA -> CD: Build backend image
  CD -> GHCR: Push freshfood-backend:<sha>
else pull_request
  GHA -> GHA: Skip image push
end

note right of CD
As-is:
- Workflow build/push image only
- Chua co step deploy backend\n(staging/prod)
end note

@enduml
